# roman-forum

roman-form is a simple API allowing consumers to manage topics and posts in a forum.

Some of the api needs authentication, please see the *Login* section if the endpoint needs authentication.

You can play with the real data in this website, it uses a demo built at https://roman-forum.herokuapp.com/

# Data Structures

## TopicSimple
+ id: 42 (number)
+ title: Hello World (string)
+ posts_count: 1 (number)
+ inserted_at: `2016-10-26T03:37:51`
+ last_post_user_name: Ming
+ last_posted_at: `2016-10-26T03:37:51`

## PostSimple
+ id: 100 (number)
+ content: "Some reply" (string)
+ inserted_at: `2016-10-26T03:37:51`
+ updated_at: `2016-10-26T03:37:51`
+ topic_id: 100

## PostItem
+ id: 100 (number)
+ content: "Some reply" (string)
+ post_user_name: "Ming" (string)
+ inserted_at: `2016-10-26T03:37:51`

## TopicDetail
+ id: 42 (number)
+ title: Hello World (string)
+ content: Content of this topic (string)
+ posts_count: 1 (number)
+ inserted_at: `2016-10-26T03:37:51`
+ last_post_user_name: Ming
+ last_posted_at: `2016-10-26T03:37:51`
+ posts (array[PostItem]) - A collection of post


## Registration [/api/register/]

### Register a User [POST]

Register a user throught the API. You should pass the user credentials in the http POST body, and
you will get a `jwt` token with expiration time.

The `jwt` token is used for authentication; you need to add the authentication header, for example:

`Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJVc2VyOjEyIiwiZXhwIjoxNDgwMDc2MDExLCJpYXQiOjE0Nzc0ODQwMTEsImlzcyI6IlJvbWFuIiwianRpIjoiZmMzYjkxYmUtMTU1OC00NmVlLWEzYTgtYTg3MmY2ZGRkMTkzIiwicGVtIjp7fSwic3ViIjoiVXNlcjoxMiIsInR5cCI6ImFjY2VzcyJ9.ftbwm6_Z0pWUPpwW5eQHpHW2mSzVtOJH1Y7degH5Jx5aPnymyBNj3liymgNZCNKhMCL6u3GRHiChkLGTu8RzLg` for endpoint that needs authentication.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "user":  {
              "name": "test_user_name",
              "password": "test_password"
            }
        }

        
+ Response 201 (applicaiton/json)

        {
            "jwt": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJVc2VyOjEyIiwiZXhwIjoxNDgwMDc2MDExLCJpYXQiOjE0Nzc0ODQwMTEsImlzcyI6IlJvbWFuIiwianRpIjoiZmMzYjkxYmUtMTU1OC00NmVlLWEzYTgtYTg3MmY2ZGRkMTkzIiwicGVtIjp7fSwic3ViIjoiVXNlcjoxMiIsInR5cCI6ImFjY2VzcyJ9.ftbwm6_Z0pWUPpwW5eQHpHW2mSzVtOJH1Y7degH5Jx5aPnymyBNj3liymgNZCNKhMCL6u3GRHiChkLGTu8RzLg",
