## Topics [/api/topics]

### List All Topics [GET]

List all topics.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (array[TopicSimple])
    

### Create a New Topic [POST]

Authentication required. Create a new topic.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJVc2VyOjEyIiwiZXhwIjoxNDgwMDc2MDExLCJpYXQiOjE0Nzc0ODQwMTEsImlzcyI6IlJvbWFuIiwianRpIjoiZmMzYjkxYmUtMTU1OC00NmVlLWEzYTgtYTg3MmY2ZGRkMTkzIiwicGVtIjp7fSwic3ViIjoiVXNlcjoxMiIsInR5cCI6ImFjY2VzcyJ9.ftbwm6_Z0pWUPpwW5eQHpHW2mSzVtOJH1Y7degH5Jx5aPnymyBNj3liymgNZCNKhMCL6u3GRHiChkLGTu8RzLg

    + Body

            {
                "topic" => {
                    "title": "Some nice title for the topic",
                    "content": "Some nice content for the topic"
                }
            }
            
+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body
    
            + Attributes (TopicSimple)


## Topic [/api/topics/{topic_id}]

### Show a Topic [GET]

Show a topic's details including each post's information.

+ Parameters

    + topic_id - Unique id for this topic

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (array[TopicDetail])
        

### Update a Topic [PUT]

Authentication required. Update a topic's title or content.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJVc2VyOjEyIiwiZXhwIjoxNDgwMDc2MDExLCJpYXQiOjE0Nzc0ODQwMTEsImlzcyI6IlJvbWFuIiwianRpIjoiZmMzYjkxYmUtMTU1OC00NmVlLWEzYTgtYTg3MmY2ZGRkMTkzIiwicGVtIjp7fSwic3ViIjoiVXNlcjoxMiIsInR5cCI6ImFjY2VzcyJ9.ftbwm6_Z0pWUPpwW5eQHpHW2mSzVtOJH1Y7degH5Jx5aPnymyBNj3liymgNZCNKhMCL6u3GRHiChkLGTu8RzLg
            
    + Body

            {
                "topic": {
                    "title": "Some nice title for the topic",
                    "content": "Some nice content for the topic"
                }
            }
            
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            + Attributes (TopicSimple)
            


